" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-7d84a0e3\" data-id=\"7d84a0e3\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3b03ce7f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3b03ce7f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Irma Gonzalez has been a full-time Realtor\u00ae since 2013. She has worked and lived in the\u00a0 Austin\u00a0&amp; Round Rock Metro for over 25 years. Prior to becoming a Realtor\u00ae, Irma obtained a bachelors and masters degree in Accounting from the University of Texas at Austin and practiced as a CPA for over 10 years. After moving 6 times in 20 years, she understands the emotional and financial stress involved in buying, selling, and moving. Irma&#8217;s first hand experience allowed her to recognize the financial and emotional impact of having the right Realtor\u00ae on your team. Irma brings attention to detail and an analytical frame of mind to her business interactions. She listens to her clients&#8217; goals, explains their options, and helps them attain the best possible outcome.\u00a0She enjoys building her business by referral through clients, friends, and family who have been delighted working with her due to her exceptional customer service and knowledge.\u00a0 Irma has invested a significant amount of time in becoming an expert in all phases of the real estate transaction in order to better serve her clients. Her in-depth-training combined with her experience ensures her clients get the best representation and advice.\u00a0<br \/><br \/>Personal Mission Statement<br \/>\u201cTo help her clients build wealth through homeownership and Real Estate investments.\u201d<br \/><br \/>Personal<\/p><p>In her free time, she enjoys spending time with her family, traveling, skiing, scuba diving, hiking, and relaxing. If you&#8217;re looking for a professional who will take great pride in helping you with your real estate needs in the Austin Metro Area, don&#8217;t hesitate to contact her at 512-699-4758 or <a title=\"mailto:irmag.realty@gmail.com\" href=\"mailto:irmag.realty@gmail.com\">irmag.realty@gmail.com<\/a>.<\/p><p><strong>Email:<a title=\"mailto:irmag.realty@gmail.com\" href=\"mailto:irmag.realty@gmail.com\">irmag.realty@gmail.com<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-751ececf elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"751ececf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<style>\n.elementor-column.elementor-col-33 ul.elementor-icon-list-items {\n    padding-bottom: 10px;\n}    \n<\/style>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Our Agents Irma Gonzalez Broker Associate Contact Irma Gonzalez has been a full-time Realtor\u00ae since 2013. She has worked and lived in the\u00a0 Austin\u00a0&amp; Round Rock Metro for over 25 years. Prior to becoming a Realtor\u00ae, Irma obtained a bachelors and masters degree in Accounting from the University of Texas at Austin and practiced as [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"elementor_header_footer","meta":{"_vp_format_video_url":"","_vp_image_focal_point":[],"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-68